snippet.title: Spirit of the North 2 | Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Greetings Guardians,

Thank you for your patience, it is not long now before Spirit of the North 2 releases on the 8th of May.

Wishlist it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1778840/Spirit_of_the_North_2/
